{
  "text": "The interviewer pairs were trained in the BIC-Q assessment by two of the authors (DZ and AEZ). During a field study, a protocol was developed in order to ensure uniform practices among the interviewer pairs. On-the-job training during the field study was focused on providing detailed clarifications for the scores [CITATION_1] . The data in this study consist of BIC-Qs that were completed after the field study, thus without any outside involvement by the authors.",
